verses.verse: Praise<WH1984> the Lord!<WH3050> Praise<WH1984> the Lord<WH3068> from the heavens;<WH8064> Praise<WH1984> Him in the heights!<WH4791>

Praise<WH1984> Him, sun<WH8121> and moon;<WH3394> Praise<WH1984> Him, all<WH3605> stars<WH3556> of light!<WH216>
